<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li><p>Students may sort by: length, height, width, or area.</p><ul>
<li><p>Rectangles with the same area:</p>
<ul>
<li>Area 12 square units: 3 by 4 (A), 12 by 1 (C)</li>
<li>Area 16 square units: 2 by 8 (D), 4 by 4 (E)</li>
<li>Area 24 square units: 8 by 3 (B), 2 by 12 (F)</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
      </li>
      <li><p>Sample responses: </p><ul>
<li>Area 12 square units: 2 by 6</li>
<li>Area 16 square units: 1 by 16</li>
<li>Area 24 square units: 4 by 6, 1 by 24</li>
</ul>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


